title: Quick Release Spring Training Series
description: 4 Week training series.  Five events per week:  A, B, C, Women Only, Junior Under 16
course: 1 KM, closed 3-lanes wide with 2 90 degree and 2 sweeping turns.  Direction reverses each week.
registration: On-line, mail, or in person.  Weekly Fees:  $15 for Ann Arbor Velo Club members, $20 for non members, $10 for first time racers including coaching clinic; free to Juniors under 16.
notes: Safe, fast training races, designed for first time racers and as early season training for more experienced riders.
directions: Runway Plaze Worksenter.  One mile south of I-94 at the State Street Exit, Ann Arbor.  Across from the Ann Arbor Airport.
